name: Shipping Upgrade
description:
Need your order faster? Add this to your cart! 

This will allow your order to ship USPS Priority Mail with a 2-3 business day delivery instead of the normal First Class mail which takes 2-5 business days. 

Not applicable for international orders or larger/heavier orders, such as a sweatshirt or 3+ apparel items. Please contact if you need special shipping arrangements or have questions if your order will qualify.

Nana is the perfect nursemaid for tucking your children in at night, ensuring they take their daily medicine, and cleaning up any messes your little Darlings may have left behind. Nana's Nursery: Caring for your little Darlings since 1953. Light heathered tee available in women's and men's styles 4.5 oz 100% cotton Women's Sizes

description:
Orders placed after December 17th cannot be guaranteed by Christmas due to high volumes of packages during the holidays. International orders will most likely arrive in January. However! We have added the option below to add Priority shipping to your order! Details here. Celebrate the return of the lost princess! A top fit for Rapunzel and everyone in her kingdom. This Tangled inspired piece features a bright golden sun on true purple dolman top. This shirt is an open-hemmed, light-weight sweatshirt material that is flowy enough for sunny days, but also provides a hip layering piece for those cooler fall days! Limited quantities available. 50/50 cotton blend. Screen printed.

name: Merida's Arrow Necklace
description:
There are those who say fate is something beyond our command. That destiny is not our own, but I know better. Our fate lives within us, you only have to be brave enough to see it. 

Determine your own fate with this dainty silver arrow on a thin link chain. 

1" arrow charm.
16" chain. 
Spring ring closure. 

Inspired by Pixar's Brave.

name: Tic Toc Croc Necklace
description:
Why, Captain, cutting your hand off was only a childish prank, you might say. 

Aye, but throwing it to that crocodile! That cursed beast liked the taste of me so well he's followed me ever since, licking his chops for the rest of me. 

And he would've had you by now, Captain, if he hadn't swallowed that alarm clock. But now, when he's about, he'd warn you, as you might say, with his tick-tock, tick-tock, tick-tock...


This bronze necklace features the infamous crocodile wrapped around the clock that warned Hook when he was nearby.

1.5" tall pendant. 
16" chain.
Lobster claw closure. 

Inspired by Peter Pan.

name: Elephant Graveyard Necklace
description:
An elephant graveyard is no place for a young prince...

This Lion King inspired necklace features a faux-bone elephant with two charms on brown cording. 

1.5" wide elephant pendant. 
16" cord.
Spring ring closure.

name: Neverland Beanie
description: Orders placed after December 17th cannot be guaranteed by Christmas due to high volumes of packages during the holidays. International orders will most likely arrive in January. However! We have added the option below to add Priority shipping to your order! Details here. But, Peter, how do we get to Neverland? Fly, of course! Take off to Neverland with this Peter inspired beanie. Newly upgraded! Limited quantities available. Slouch style beanie 55% acrylic 45% polyester 5" red feather embroidered design Keep up to date with new inventory at the Whosits + Whatsits Facebook page

name: Shadow Man's Voodoo Necklace
description:
That's an echo, gentlemen. Just a little something we have here in Louisiana, a little parlor trick. Don't worry... Now you can get what you want without losing what you had from this Dr. Facilier inspired necklace. An adjustable cloth cord carries your dark magic resin pendant to call on your friends from the other side.* Shortest cord length: 18" Longest cord length: 34" Pendant length: 2.5" Princess and the Frog inspired.



*Whosits is not liable for any spells or curses summoned by this necklace.

name: Hakuna Matata Beanie
description:
It means no worries- for the rest of your days! 

Limited quantities available.

8.5" in length
100% acrylic
Slogan embroidered design in two-tone gold and yellow.

Lion King inspired.

name: Mermaid Cuff
description:
For every fish under (and out of) the sea! 

This silver fish scale cuff is perfect for all us little mermaids who are waiting to find a witch and get fins of our own. Ariel doesn't know how good she had it.

One size fits most. 
Due to the nature of this cuff, it can bend to accommodate any size wrist!

Back in stock mid-September.

name: Be Our Guest Necklace
description:
Ma chere Mademoiselle, it is with deepest pride and greatest pleasure that we welcome you tonight. And now we invite you to relax, let us pull up a  chair as the dining room proudly presents - the Be Our Guest Necklace!

A bronze chain features an acrylic yellow rose pendant complete with one of Belle's gracious hosts, Lumière. 

Chain length: Approx 22" 
Pendant diameter: 1.5" 

Inspired by Beauty and the Beast.

name: The Pan Sweatshirt
description:
The next of the limited edition sweatshirts is here! It features none other than everyone's favorite Peter Pan. This over-sized image pops with crazy vibrant color. Each item is hand air-brushed by Richard Mink making every one a truly one of a kind piece. Only 10 available in the unisex sizes listed below. There will be no additional pieces made making this a very special, ultra limited edition item. 50/50 Poly Cotton blend. For airbrush care, please visit our FAQ page.

name: Tea Party Necklace
description:
Would you like a little more tea?
Well, I haven't had any yet, so I can't very well take more.
Ah, you mean you can't very well take less.
Yes. You can always take more than nothing.

What fun is a mad tea party without a cup of tea! Luckily for you, this little teacup is full and ready to go. It's paired with a teapot so you'll never have to wait for more! 

CLEAN CUP!
MOVE DOWN!  

Teacup pendant diameter: 1"
Chain length: 18"

name: Robin Hood Storybook Necklace
description:
Before they found a place in our hearts in the form we know them now, our favorite childhood stories were just that- storybooks! 

The Robin Hood book pendant features a bow and arrow on the front and more ammunition on the back cover. It's paired with a crown charm. 

Pendant dimensions: 3/4" x 1"
Chain length: 18" 
Ball chain closure.

name: Nightmare Before Christmas Pocket Watch
description:
'Twas a long time ago, longer now than it seems in a place perhaps you've seen in your dreams. Or perhaps you've simplye lost track of time completely without this pocket watch. 

Halloweentime is approaching and what better way to celebrate than with this Pumpkin King tombstone watch! An extra long chain features a bronze and pewter finished pocket watch with Jack Skellington. Patchwork pattern continued on reverse size. 

Chain length: 31"
Watch diameter: ~2"
Batteries included.

name: Tiger Lily Ring
description:
To the very first Injun prince, he kissed a maid and start to blush
And we've all been blushin' since
You've got it from the headman
The real true story of the red man
No matter what's been written or said
Now you know why the red man's red!

Inspired by the beautiful but brave Native American princess Tiger Lily- one of the allies to Peter Pan and the Lost Boys. 

A bright turquoise gem pairs with an antiqued bronze feather to create this double-layered ring. 

One size fits most. Approximately size 5.5

name: Wish Upon a Starfish Necklace
description:
Perfect for your under the sea ball! This charming silver tone starfish is adorned with white rhinestones and uniquely shaped pearl drop. Every little mermaid is waiting to get her fins on it. 

Pendant width: 1.5"
Chain length: 16"

name: Lost Boy Ring
description:
I think I had a mother once.
What was she like?
I forget.
I had a white rat.
That's no mother!

Fall in rank and follow Captain Peter Pan with the Lost Boy Ring! Ring features two animal ears to embody your favorite lost boy spirit animal. 

One size fits most. Approximately size 6/7.

Available in antiqued gold and silver tones.

name: Aladdin's Golden Scarab Ring
description:
If you seek the Cave of Wonders on your journey through Agrabah, look no further weary travelers for you have uncovered both scarab halves and your treasure now awaits you. 

Of course, only if you're the diamond in the rough. 

One size fits most.
Approximately size 7. 

Aladdin inspired.

name: Spoonful of Sugar Necklace
description:
In every job that must be done, there is an element of fun. 
Find the fun aaaand snap! The job's a game! 

In honor of the upcoming release of Saving Mr. Banks, we are happy to introduce the Spoonful of Sugar necklace. A single golden spoon is filled with a sugary white rhinestone. Mary Poppins herself would be proud! 

Pendant length: 1.5"
Chain length: 19"
Toggle closure.

name: Colors of The Wind Necklace
description:
Come run the hidden pine trails of the forest
Come taste the sunsweet berries of the Earth
Come roll in all the riches all around you
And for once, never wonder what they're worth

You will undoubtedly hear the wolf cry with this extra long Pocahontas inspired necklace. A never-ending circle of orange and red stones fill this silver pendant with two acrylic leaves. 

Pendant diameter: 1.75"
Chain length: 24"
Toggle closure

name: You've Got a Friend in Me Bracelets
description:
You've got troubles, well I've got 'em too
There isn't anything I wouldn't do for you
We stick together and we see it through
You've got a friend in me

Woody + Buzz Lightyear Best Friend bracelets! Order comes with 1 Woody and 1 Buzz bracelet. One size fits most.

Red/yellow design.
White/navy design.

name: Snow White Storybook Necklace
description:
Before they found a place in our hearts in the form we know them now, our favorite childhood stories were just that- storybooks! 

The Snow White book pendant features the notorious poison apple! It's paired with a heart charm after all that wishing for the one she loves. 

Pendant dimensions: 3/4" x 1"
Chain length: 18" 
Ball chain closure.

name: Aurora Wonders Necklace
description:
I wonder why each 
Little bird has someone
To sing to sweet things to
A gay little love melody?
I wonder, I wonder
If my heart keeps singing
Will my song go winging
To someone who'll find me
And bring back a love song to me?

Deep in the forest, Briar Rose daydreams before joining this little owl and her other forest friends in a dance wonderfully interrupted by a prince! And this featured friend couldn't look more enchanted.

Pendant length: 2.5"
Chain length: 29"
Lobster claw closure.

name: Princess  Ring
description:
Once there was a princess. And she fell in love. It was very easy! Nearly as easy as it is to fall in love with this ring fit for any soon-to-be royal. 

A rose-gold toned tiara ring sparkles with white rhinestones. Perfect for the princess in all of us! 

One size fits most. 
Approximately size 6.

name: Peter Pan Storybook Necklace
description:
Before they found a place in our hearts in the form we know them now, our favorite childhood stories were just that- storybooks! 

The Peter Pan book pendant features Captain Hook's pirate ship on the front and hook and knife logo on the back cover. It's paired with a little Tinkerbell charm. 

Pendant also pays tribute to the author of the original Peter Pan, J. M. Barrie, on the spine. 

Pendant dimensions: 3/4" x 1"
Chain length: 18" 
Ball chain closure.

name: Sassy Tink Necklace
description:
Fairies have to be one thing or the other, because being so small they unfortunately have room for one feeling only at a time. And in this case, Tinkerbell isn't too happy about the Wendy bird. 

Bronze chain necklace features sassy Tink in a red rhinestone dress and white rhinestone wings. She dangles with a few of her trinkets- an acorn and red button.

Chain length: 27"
Tink pendant length: 3"

name: Cinderella Storybook Necklace
description:
Before they found a place in our hearts in the form we know them now, our favorite childhood stories were just that- storybooks! 

The Cinderella book pendant features a glass slipper on the front and grandfather clock on the back. It's paired with the key Jaq and Gus retrieved to set her free.  

Pendant dimensions: 3/4" x 1"
Chain length: 18" 
Ball chain closure.

name: Pan's Feather Necklace
description:
"Now," said he, "shall I give you a kiss?" and she replied with a slight primness, "If you please." She made herself rather cheap by inclining her face toward him, but he merely dropped an acorn button into her hand, so she slowly returned her face to where it had been before, and said nicely that she would wear his kiss on the chain around her neck.

Now you can wear a kiss from Peter around your neck.

This bronze necklace features a feather pendant with cutout detail and acorn charm. 

Chain length: 27"
Feather length: 2.5"

name: Happily Ever After Necklace
description:
We all know how the story ends. Time to add a little of that magic to yours! 

Ride off into the sunset with this antiqued bronze Happily Ever After layered necklace. A heart charm completes the enchantment. 

Shortest chain length: 16"
Longest chain length: 20"

name: That's Demented Shirt
description: Likes you? Please, Rapunzel. That's demented. Mother knows best. Distressed design on thin black scoop neck shirt. 100% cotton. This shirt is not screen printed and it is not airbrushed. The design is made by treating the color of the actual t-shirt. It cannot fade, wash away, etc. Because the fabric itself is treated, the fibers of the design are slightly weakened. After many washes and wears, you may experience some distressed holes. The over all design and colors will differ from shirt to shirt. That's the beauty of handmade! Each shirt will have different spray patterns, bits of over spray and slightly different placement making each shirt one of a kind. It has never been more true with this shirt! No two shirts will be the same. Inspired by Tangled, Rapunzel and Mother Gothel.

name: Snake in my Boot Necklace
description:
Everyone's favorite deputy brings this rootin, tootin necklace to Whosits + Whatsits! 

A bronze ball chain features a bronze cowboy hat coupled with a rocking horse charm and Woody's very own sheriff badge complete with white rhinestone accent. 

Chain length: Approx 22"
Cowboy hat length: 1.5"
 

Inspire by Sheriff Woody of Toy Story.

name: Maleficent Ring
description:
You poor, simple fools. Thinking you could defeat me- The Mistress of All Evil! This truly wicked claw ring embodies everything that is the epitome of Princess Aurora's demise.

Pewter-toned ring with black rhinestones. 

Diameter of the inside is 1.1 cm, or approximately a size 0. Recommended for slender fingers.

name: Peter's Kiss Necklace
description:
Need to give a kiss to somebody? Or take one, perhaps, from a lost boy?

This antiqued gold-tone acorn hangs from an extra long ball chain. 

Pendant length: 1"
Chain length: 27"

Inspired by Peter Pan and Wendy Darling

name: Prince John's Jewels Necklace
description: Oh, poppycock. Female bandits? What next? Rubbish. Here you can take what Robin Hood and Little John left behind after ransacking the prince in the middle of Sherwood Forest. Mother did always like Richard the most... A bronze necklace with crown and red and green jewels. 18" chain. The crown 0.7" in diameter (the size of a US dime coin).

name: Key to the Haunted Mansion
description:
Welcome, foolish mortals, to the Haunted Mansion. I am your host, your... ghost host. Kindly step all the way in please and make room for everyone. There's no turning back now...

Unlock the happy haunts of the Haunted Mansion with this ghoulish key. The bronze pendant hangs from an extra long gold and black chain.  

2.5" long key pendant. 
24" chain.
Lobster claw closure.

name: Pride Rock Shirt
description: Asante sana. Squash banana. Red design on 100% cotton white scoop neck tee with raw edge hem. This shirt is NOT screen printed. All of my shirts are air-brushed by hand. Check the FAQ's for details on wear and care! The over all design and color will differ slightly from shirt to shirt. That's the beauty of handmade! Each shirt will have different spray patterns, bits of over spray and slightly different placement making each shirt one of a kind. Inspired by The Lion King.

name: Pinocchio's Companions Ring
description:
This dainty ring will satisfy the most classic Disney fans by bringing Figaro and Celo together at last! 

Gold-toned, open ring features the tiniest little Cleo paired next to an enamel black and white Figaro with blue eyes. Simply adorable! 

One size fits most. Ring size is slightly adjustable due to it's open nature- just gently widen to fit whatever finger you'd like! 
Recommended for ring sizes between 5 and 8.

name: The Sea Witch Necklace
description:
Beluga, Sevruga
Come winds of the Caspian Sea
Larynxes, glossitis
Et Max Laryngitis
La voce to me

This Little Mermaid inspired necklace features the shell Ursula used to capture Ariel's voice on super soft black suede lace. 

16" length.
Spring ring closure.

name: Be Prepared Shirt
description:
Be king undisputed. Respected, saluted. And seen for the wonder I am. Yes, my teeth and ambitions are bared: Be prepare. Orange design on triple blend tangerine v-neck tee. This shirt is NOT screen printed. All of my shirts are air-brushed by hand. Check the FAQ's for details on wear and care! The over all design and color will differ slightly from shirt to shirt. That's the beauty of handmade! Each shirt will have different spray patterns, bits of over spray and slightly different placement making each shirt one of a kind. Inspired by The Lion King.

name: Cinderella's Mice Ring
description:
Poor Cinderelly. Ev'ry time she find a minute, that's the time when they begin it. "Cinderelly! Cinderelly!"

Have your own little pal to help you get ready for the ball! A tiny little mouse will wrap itself around you from head to tail.

One size fits most. Ring size is slightly adjustable due to it's open nature- just gently widen to fit whatever finger you'd like! 
Recommended for ring sizes between 5 and 8.

name: Minnie's Bow
description: A bow Minnie Mouse herself would envy! A vivid red and white polka dot scrunchie features wire in the bow to position however you'd like.

name: Merida's Arrow Cuff
description:
I don't want to get married! I want to stay single and let my hair flow in the wind as I ride through the glen firing arrows into the sunset. You can, too, capture the spirit of Merida with this bracelet. 

An antiqued cuff feature celtic arrow head design and 3 little blue wisps so you can start your very own adventure!  

2.5" diameter. 
One size fits most. Metal can slightly bend for larger or smaller fit. 
And take warning! Merida has just sharpened these arrow tips.

name: The Evil Queen Necklace
description:
Slave in the magic mirror, come from the farthest space, through wind and darkness I summon thee. Speak! Let me see thy face.

We all have a little dark side. And when you need to embody Snow White's  villainess, just throw this necklace on. A burnt orange resin gem in ornate antiqued gold pendant. 

Pendant length: 2.5"
Chain length: 29"

name: Briar Rose Necklace
description:
Before she was Sleeping Beauty, Aurora was known to her fairy friends as Briar Rose. 

Our Briar Rose necklace embodies all the elegance this hidden princess brought to the forest with an ivory acrylic rose in an antiqued bronze base. 

Pendant length: 2.25"
Chain length: 30"

name: Daisy Duck Couture Heels
description:
Inspired by everyone's favorite lady duck, Daisy. 

Two-tone purple round toe heels with suede and faux patent leather. Each shoe features a white satin bow with Daisy pink trim and would not be complete without duck tail feathers on the heel. 

Did you know that Daisy Duck is starting to come back out at Disneyland? She'd love to see you wearing these in the park!

name: Paperman Necklace
description: A paper plane charm with red accent on silver toned chain. 16" chain length. Spring ring closure.

name: The Little Mermaid Storybook Necklace
description:
Before they found a place in our hearts in the form we know them now, our favorite childhood stories were just that- storybooks! 

The Little Mermaid book pendant features a mermaid tail on the front and little shells on the back cover. It's paired with an open clam shell charm. 

Pendant also pays tribute to the author of the original Little Mermaid on the spine. 

Pendant dimensions: 1" x 1.5"
Chain length: 18" 
Ball chain closure.

name: Neverland Ring
description:
Introducing the Neverland ring! A charming charm ring inspired by Peter Pan.

This ring features 3 green glass beads, a silver-tone leaf and bronze star with red enamel inlay. 

One size fits most. Rings are adjustable.

name: Wonderland Necklace
description:
If I had a world of my own, everything would be nonsense. Nothing would be what it is because everything would be what it isn't. And contrary-wise; what it is it wouldn't be, and what it wouldn't be, it would. You see?

Step into your own Wonderland or host your own tea party with this Alice inspired necklace. A light-blue suede lace features a bow pendant and pearl accent. 

Suede length: 18"
Bow length: 1"

name: Tesseract Necklace
description:
The Tesseract has awakened. It is on a little world, a human world. They wield its power, but our ally is working knows it's working, so that they never will learn.

Harness the power of the Tesseract with this glass capsule necklace featuring a hand-painted square glass bead. 

Chain length: 18"
Capsule pendant length: 1.25"

name: You're My Only Friend Abu Necklace
description:
Oh it's sad Aladdin hit the bottom! 

Take home Aladdin's only friend- well until, ya know...the Genie and Jasmine and carpet and Raja...actually he becomes quite popular. But it all started with one apple stealing little monkey. 

A bronze 3D Abu charm (holding that little stolen apple) is paired with color coordinating gems and a diamond in the rough. 

Chain length: 18"
Spring closure.
